title: New: birthday – Parade
content:
Oakland’s Duran Visek aka birthday is like a meticulously crafted amalgamation of a whole myriad of artists – from the subtle pop of Troye Sivan to the heartfelt emotional pleas of Youth Lagoon, he bares all on latest track Parade.

With an EP set to be released before the end of the year, 2017 is already shaping up to be a big year for the twenty one year old. Check out Parade below.
